name: Botik
body:
### Bari Galus
This is the website for Games bot located in #ArmChat,'s games room #Xaxatun on [Hye Chat](http://www.hye.cnat/) a bot. We present text and files that has answers to all questions in Games. Channel operators appreciate your collaborative interests in assisting to enhance games questions and answers. We do however ask you to please do not use the answers to boost your game scores.

If you intend to play `Games` in #Xaxatun we ask you to please do not continue any further than this page. However, if your intentions are to help enhance the bots, we appreciate your efforts and welcome all your inputs. Our recommendation is to edit it on GitHub site, but if you're a PRO then download Zip and make installations in your computer.

All collaborative editing are through Github. You may edit or submit edit requests. Once again Thank you for your efforts.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble? Please join us in [Hye Chat](http://www.hye.chat/chat)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
